code: @Test public void testNoFeedInHeader() throws Exception {     MockEndpoint mock = getMockEndpoint("mock:result").     mock.expectedMessageCount(1).     mock.assertIsSatisfied().     Exchange exchange = mock.getExchanges().get(0).     Message in = exchange.getIn().     assertNotNull(in).     assertNull(in.getHeader(RssConstants.RSS_FEED)). }

protected RouteBuilder createRouteBuilder() throws Exception {     return new RouteBuilder() {          public void configure() throws Exception {             from("rss:file:src/test/data/rss20.xml?splitEntries=false&consumer.delay=500&feedHeader=false").to("mock:result").         }     }. }
